Package: twfy
Title: Drive the API for TheyWorkForYou
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Will", "Lowe", email = "wlowe@princeton.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R wrapper around the API of TheyWorkForYou, a parliamentary 
    monitoring site that scrapes and repackages Hansard (the UK's parliamentary 
    record) and augments it with information from the Register of Members' 
    Interests, election results, and voting records to provide a unified 
    source of information about UK legislators and their activities. See 
    <http://www.theyworkforyou.com> for details.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    httr,
    jsonlite
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
